<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What You Can Expect From Corporate Event DJ Misha</h2>

<p>DJ Misha brings <a href="/services/">the perfect blend of energy and entertainment</a> to your corporate event, making it a blast for every guest who attends. A dynamic blend of modern dance music along with all of the hits to get the whole crowd moving are at the core of a meticulously crafted set from DJ Misha. Coupled with the experience of hundreds of performances for hosts like <a href="https://home.kpmg/xx/en/home.html">KPMG</a>, <a href="https://www.sisley-paris.com/en-US/">Sisley Skincare</a> of Paris, Intel, <a href="https://www.princess-hotels.com/en/">Princess Hotels</a> and Banana Republic, plus the euphoric vibes of a festival DJ, and you have an experience that can only be found at a DJ Misha performance. Add a live saxophone into the mix and watch as your guests enjoy a night like never before.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">DJ Services Also Include</h3>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A polished and multidimensional DJ set featuring an expertly crafted collection of modern dance music — crowd-pumping pop, electronic, funk, disco and hip-hop tracks with groovy basslines, perfect hooks, flowing beats and the perfect vibe for your corporate event.</li><li>The ability to perform anywhere your event is located</li><li><a href="https://wearecrossfader.co.uk/all-reviews/">Best-in-class DJ equipment</a>, such as up to 4 JBL speakers (1000 watt), 2 Technics turntables, Rane and Pioneer DJ mixers. Shure wireless microphones are also included for making announcements and engaging the crowd.</li><li>Additional corporate event entertainment, such as live sax and dj packages or even a full-sized band, can bring even more excitement to the night.</li><li>Equipment setup 1.5 hours before the event and post-event breakdown included</li><li>Optional DJ event insurance&nbsp;</li><li>Top-tier, honest professionalism and seamless execution from a DJ who has performed at hundreds of corporate events, private parties, weddings, festivals and nightclubs</li><li>Optional equipment, including dance lighting and fog machines, are also available from partnering vendors.</li><li>A corporate event your guests will be thrilled they experienced</li></ul>

