<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What Does a Corporate Event DJ Do?</h2>

<p>Corporate event DJs come in many forms but have two responsibilities at their core. First is to craft a collection of excellent music that can make specific audiences energetic. The second is to continuously program and mix music together to create a <a href="https://www.djtoptips.com/create-best-dj-set/">seamless DJ set</a> that is perfectly dialed into the energy of the crowd and the event's hosts, regardless of if they're performing in a nightclub or at a corporate event. Ultimately, the most important thing is to ensure the crowd is having fun, dancing their hearts out and keeping the party alive — values DJ Misha has built his entire career around.</p>

<p><strong>Central to DJ Misha's corporate event performances are:</strong></p>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>A collection of recorded tracks across genres that are programmed to create the perfect set for your audience's experience.</li><li>The development of a musical ear and an understanding of each song's structure, leading to a selection of songs that are in key and complimentary to create a rhythmic merge.</li><li>A high degree of professionalism and communication with the event's hosts to ensure the energy and music being performed matches the vision the hosts intend for their corporate event.</li><li>An expert understanding of all equipment involved, like turntables, mixers and amplifiers.</li><li>A personality that <a href="/">connects with the audience</a> to play the perfect blend of music to create an enthusiastic atmosphere that goes above and beyond other corporate events.</li><li>The ability to improvise, bring originality to any set and connect with the crowd, key to any DJ's live performance, regardless of setting.</li><li>Keeping the music at appropriate volume at all times throughout the event.&nbsp;</li><li>Comfort with taking on MC duties to make announcements as needed and keep the event flowing in the right direction. </li></ul>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What is Included In a Mobile DJ Package</h3>

<p>A dynamic performance from DJ Misha is available for your corporate event — regardless of what side of the country it's occurring. <a href="/prices/">Mobile DJ packages</a> vary depending on the equipment needed for the event, travel required to the event and vendors that may be collaborated with at the event but are guaranteed to be exceptional for all who attend. Mobile corporate event DJ packages include:</p>

<ul class="wp-block-list"><li>The same exciting performance with access to the same vast collection of music to set the perfect atmosphere for the event</li><li>Exceptional DJ equipment from top vendors in the country, including top-of-the line speakers, mixers, turntables and microphones</li><li>Live saxophonists and musicians are also available for travel</li><li>All travel pre-arranged, including necessary air travel, ground travel by car, lodging and all meals&nbsp;</li><li>Communication with all other event vendors to coordinate equipment needs, timelines and other event specifics</li><li>Set-up 1.5 hours before music begins and breakdown included with each event</li></ul>

<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Corporate Event DJ FAQs</h2>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What types of corporate events will DJ perform?</h3>

<p>There are no limits when it comes to the types of corporate events that DJ Misha will perform at! With plenty of experience performing at experiences from corporate festival outings to store openings and conferences, DJ Misha is well-versed in developing a one-of-a-kind show that can make your event stand out from any corporate event your guests have attended previously. Several options are available for customizing your night, including flexible performance of diverse music styles, MC duties and the addition of a live saxophone player.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How do DJs do corporate events?</h3>

<p>What separates DJ Misha's corporate events from the others is the level of care that goes into making every performance perfect for your particular crowd. Every set list is curated to your crowd's music taste and the vibe you would like to create at your event, with the opportunity to discuss the direction for the music at your event available as well. Plus, the option to add on live saxophone players and other musicians is available to bring even more energy to an exceptional night.&nbsp;</p>

<div class="home-testi testi-full">
	<center>
	<p>His music got everyone on the dance floor, and we were there for hours! It was so much fun! 
	<br><br>
