<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can DJ Misha travel to my corporate event?</h3>

<p>Yes! DJ Misha is based in San Diego but is available for travel anywhere within the United States or even internationally, either by ground or by air. Travel details will be arranged at the time of booking.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What kind of music will DJ Misha perform at my corporate event?</h3>

<p>When booking your corporate event, we begin with a discussion about the overall vision you have for your event, along with general details about your guests, demographics and their tastes. DJ Misha will then craft a unique DJ set and curated performance just for your event — exactly what a <a href="https://www.mi.edu/education/the-5-best-ways-to-become-a-dj/">great DJ</a> does best. Any specific songs you would love to have featured at your event can be easily worked in during the booking process.</p>

<div class="home-testi testi-full">
	<center>
	<p>Misha was great to work with. We told him the vibe we were looking for and then we played an amazing 4 hour set without any direction needed from us. Had all the people dancing. 10/10
	<br><br>
	<i class="fas fa-user"></i> Quinn T. via Google</p>
	</center>
</div>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can DJ Misha provide equipment for my corporate event? </h3>

<p>Yes! For events in the vicinity of San Diego, DJ Misha can provide all necessary equipment for your event, including a high-powered speaker system, dual turntables, lighting equipment and a vast collection of curated music. For events outside of the San Diego area, DJ Misha works with top vendors across the country to set you up with everything needed to make this corporate event a success.</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Is event insurance included with my corporate event's performance?</h3>

<p>One-day event insurance can be included as an optional add-on for any of DJ Misha's corporate events. Many venues, such as banquet rooms and hotels, require that all vendors provide evidence of insurance to protect from unlikely incidents or accidents that would stop the event or present a safety hazard.This is usually due to the venue&#8217;s own legal and insurance requirements and DJ Misha is happy to work with the venue to ensure all bases are covered.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can DJ Misha make announcements and act as an MC at my event?&nbsp;</h3>

<p>Yes, DJ Misha is happy to provide this service!&nbsp; As a Master of Ceremonies, Misha will ensure the event keeps flowing in the planned direction by keeping track of timelines, setting up music cues when needed, making announcements throughout the night and ensuring microphones are set-up and moving to the appropriate speaker at the right moment.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<h3 class="wp-block-heading">I have additional questions, can we set time up to talk?</h3>

<p>Absolutely! Visit the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> to submit a request or find other ways of getting in touch with DJ Misha.</p>

